<p>I have TreeGrid with multiple columns and I use RowEditing plugin to save data. I want to change value of "Total" dynamically when "Price" changes. I made the following, but it doesnt work.  when I look at "Total" object, I see thet value is changed, but a cant see this in RowEditing plugin at the time of editing and before update.</p>  <pre><code>{     text: 'price',             dataIndex: 'price',     editor: {     xtype: 'textfield',             listeners: {                 change: function (field, newValue, oldValue, eOpts) {                     var selectedModel = MyTree.getSelectionModel().getSelection()[0];                     selectedModel.set('total', 'Total sum is' + field.value);                 }             }     } },  {      text: 'total',             dataIndex: 'total',     editor: {         xtype: 'textfield'     } } </code></pre>